Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.25,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.80,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.38,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.97,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.97,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.89,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.31,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.78,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:03:00.66,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.58,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.92,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:21.71,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Losing his brother Ace in the great war against the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.52,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,caused Luffy to be overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.97,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But now we turn the clock back ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:32.05,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tale of how Luffy and Ace became brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.08,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.04,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,you're trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.95,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,One point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.08,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.96,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.14,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.16,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.33,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I win, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.13,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:46.82,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!  You always have a good fight, Ace and Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.60,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!  You're fighting me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.39,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be dodging?\NI won't hold back, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.52,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Your rubber-powers again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.42,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You only stretched out your fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.43,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.74,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.42,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:22.96,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But are your abilities good for anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:28.20,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!  It just won't work!\NAnd I was so close, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.97,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:33.74,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No.  One hundred fights each per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.68,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You can try again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.90,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy lost fifty times against both me and Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:42.50,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I have twenty-four wins and twenty-six losses against Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.28,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Lost by two points, huh?  Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:49.62,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You two!  I'm gonna beat the crap out of you after I turn ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.98,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be thirteen by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.29,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and get supplies for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.13,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Wanna go for some crocodiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile meat sure is tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.51,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, don't get eaten this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.72,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, you only survived because of your inflated body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.69,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch us.  You can't swim, so you'll only get in our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.63,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.27,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.31,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The harsh conditions of Mt. Corvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.57,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,made them stronger every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.19,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,To the north of this mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:51.93,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,lies the final station of uncertainty, the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And even further north...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:07:00.70,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,lies a town surrounded by a giant stone wall, completely closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:09.24,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,An entrance known as the\NGreat Gate is the only way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:15.59,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Twice a day, massive piles of trash gathered from all over the country are brought through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.12,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.58,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:28.29,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The inhabitants of the Gray Terminal will occasionally enter the town to resell goods that they find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.58,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!  What are you carrying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.38,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile skin.  I'm going to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:41.94,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.45,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Move along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.52,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once you pass through the Great Gate, you enter a wide street filled with people from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.19,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is Edge Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:06.30,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Edge Town is where the city's delinquents and hoodlums hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.16,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!  Just leave that package of yours right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.49,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.87,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you pathetic hoodlum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.77,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.97,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.65,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna rob people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.13,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,then you should choose your victims more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.95,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's the group from the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.16,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.47,Main,Luffy & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.81,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Deep within the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.79,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,another great stone wall stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:11.66,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Within these walls lies High Town,\Nwhere the royals and nobles live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this country is Goa Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:23.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It is known as the most beautiful kingdom in all of East Blue, without a single piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.93,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Even Windmill Village, where Luffy was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:33.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,is in a remote, overlooked part of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.97,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we got so much money for the crocodile skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.77,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've got even more for our Pirate Fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.43,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.11,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to eat some delicious ramen in just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.31,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen?  What's that? {...Junko Takeuchi, the voice actor of Uzumaki Naruto, just asked what ramen is. Well, there's something I never thought I'd hear...}{def:  why does the rich kid not know what ramen is?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.58,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.28,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Anything will do, I just really want some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.25,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.21,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.67,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.82,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,This restaurant doesn't serve your kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.72,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like your best private room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.17,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,T-That crest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:30.70,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Such an honor, a noble coming to our humble restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.61,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,We will prepare the room for you immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.96,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That's a handy thing you've got there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.16,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I picked it up in town earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.00,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your three orders of ramen.  Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.88,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time and enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.70,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,So this is ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It looks tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.64,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Well, try eating some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.69,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, this is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.74,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I want more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:20.70,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like another serving.  Three orders of ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.57,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.49,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Another serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.41,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.33,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Another!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.54,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes!  Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.00,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.18,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.56,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.77,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.74,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Customer, I was just told that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.63,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we're busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.72,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.16,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,They're running away without paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.28,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.35,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That ramen was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.86,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.31,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They're just kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.63,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's those three again!  They're known criminals!  Why'd you let them in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.10,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:29.01,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, please catch those three children!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.48,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they escaped through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.37,Main,Waitress,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fourth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:40.48,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,They've cost us 26 bowls of ramen and a window!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.51,Main,Waiter,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manager!  They left this note!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:46.87,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.69,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Pay us back with treasure?! { tlc: this needs to be brought out of context, otherwise it looks like HE'S saying it rather than the letter's saying it. }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.67,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.84,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.50,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.46,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.83,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.96,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sabo!  He's calling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:10.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.33,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,He must think I'm someone else.  Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.65,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.27,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:39.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:46.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.85,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What?  I'm not hiding anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.73,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he is!  Spit it out, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:08.04,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's right to keep secrets from each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:10.96,Main,Luffy & Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.21,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.76,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us, already!  I'm gonna beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.51,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.22,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,The son of a noble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.54,Main,Luffy & Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.31,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.83,Main,Luffy & Ace,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.19,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:47.03,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, both my parents are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:51.82,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an orphan, and I didn't grow up in the Gray Terminal either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.23,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The man who called out to me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.83,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:02.61,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.21,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.16,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He apologized, so it's fine, right?  I forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.76,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:14.43,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If you were born as a noble, why would you want to go to that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.89,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I ran away from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.48,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Listen close, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:33.78,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,You must acquire intelligence and manners that befit a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:37.62,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,You have to grow up to be a man who can marry into the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:42.67,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, our family's status will be secured!  And you will be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:48.93,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really become happy by marrying a girl from the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.05,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.60,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Sabo. {...So if I were to take a guess at why he ran away... Does it have anything to do with these two being FUCKING CREEPY?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.14,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.31,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.10,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.72,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,The cargo ship sank?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.59,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the lives of the crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:10.01,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,I had to pay a lot for that cargo,\Nwhat are you going to do about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.63,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?  Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.36,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:18.07,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.83,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.08,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!  I drew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.14,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired from work, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.76,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to draw a picture like this, then do some more studying in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.97,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:57.02,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a child of the royal family,\Nthat means I'm related to the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.02,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me home on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.75,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you insolent filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.26,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Are you ignoring an order from royalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.76,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.89,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the son of a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.94,Flashbacks,Royal snob,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.91,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.74,Flashbacks,Royal bitch,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he'd hurt the son of royalty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.70,Flashbacks,Royal bitch,0000,0000,0000,,He's done something completely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:42.37,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sabo!  Did you really get into a fight with this royal son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.75,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and he really hurt me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.37,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because he pulled a knife on m{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:59.39,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,I am so sorry!  I hope he's not hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.59,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,I am really, really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:05.75,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take him to see a doctor right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:09.90,Flashbacks,Sabo's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't tell anyone about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:16.50,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,All they wanted was an heir to protect their status and fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:20.95,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:28.17,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,If I couldn't marry a royal girl, I'd be trash to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.29,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, they made me study with a tutor every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:35.74,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,My parents would always fight because I wasn't good enough for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.96,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I was nothing but a bother in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:44.14,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for you two but, even with parents, I'm still alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:50.52,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that sometimes you leave the house and run off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.30,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to consider it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:57.11,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,but you must never go near the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:03.62,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,We're nobles, we live in High Town with the king and royals.  The people who live in the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.48,Flashbacks,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,are from a completely inferior world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.53,Flashbacks,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.64,Flashbacks,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep loitering around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.05,Flashbacks,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long it'll be before you're stripped and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.06,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear your stories today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:37.87,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The ones about all the different countries you've seen and visited across the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.05,Flashbacks,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are one weird kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.08,Flashbacks,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Well, alright.  Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.49,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:53.33,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The nobles despise the Gray Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.25,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd rather stay there than live a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.67,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,that's been planned decades in advance in that suffocating High Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.09,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.18,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!  Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.83,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us have to set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.35,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of this country and be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.90,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the wide world, and write a book about what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.77,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to study in preparation for the voyage, then that's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.99,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get stronger, and become pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:33.75,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'd become one even if you didn't tell me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:39.55,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a pirate, defeat everyone in my way, and become known across the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:43.13,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the proof that I lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:47.48,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if the world doesn't accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.06,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much they hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.96,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a great pirate and stand above everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.86,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run from anyone, or lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:01.84,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure the whole world knows my name, even if it's through fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.26,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:22.75,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was wondering what you'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.64,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are an interesting guy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.91,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see what the future has in store for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:35.17,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,But wait... Becoming pirates is one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:38.74,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,but all three of us want to be captain, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.49,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,An obstacle I hadn't considered...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:45.30,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, I just thought you'd be my navigator or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys come with me on my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.82,Main,Ace & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:54.25,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!  Come onboard!  Hey come on, join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.24,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That's never gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:57.81,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.38,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.32,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an interesting guy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:14.64,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can decide our future later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:18.06,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We might end up sailing on separate ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.72,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you stole that from Dadan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:24.21,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:28.94,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,When you exchange sake cups, you become brothers. {Copy-paste from 467}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers?  Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:37.33,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,When we become pirates, we might not be crewmates on the same ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.63,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,but our bonds will keep us connected as brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:44.38,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where we are or what we do, our bond will not be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:49.99,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,With this, starting today, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:52.17,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:00.82,Main,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:12.49,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of the day when they set out to sea as pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:14.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others get into all sorts of mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:19.38,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Then an attack by a certain individual threatens their peaceful life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:24.13,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and the trio are forced to say goodbye to their life with the Dadan Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.75,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell to the Dadan Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret Base is Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:31.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
